{"id":63415,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/难得一见的雪花与樱花（组图）/","date":"2010-04-25T17:00:15Z","modified":"2010-04-25T17:00:15Z","title":"难得一见的雪花与樱花（组图）","content":"<div style=\"line-height:160%;font-size:14px\">\n<p>      </p>\n<p align=\"center\"><font size=\"6\"><span><strong>难得一见的雪花与樱花（组图）</strong><strong></strong></span></font></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:22pt\"> </span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><font size=\"4\"><span>前天，我去日本东北部的郡山，那里正是樱花盛开的时节，却下起了雪，我得以看到<strong>枝头雪花压樱花</strong>的难得景致。</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"></span></font></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><font size=\"4\"><span>郡山的日本朋友告诉我，他也从来没有看到过这样的景致。</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"></span></font></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><font size=\"4\"><span>我拍了几张照片，发出来与博友共享。</span></font></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><font size=\"4\"><span></span></font> </p>\n<p align=\"left\"><font size=\"4\"><span></span></font> </p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://1812.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2010/4/24/20/14/128e268ea0cg214.jpg\" style=\"display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;text-align:center\"></font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><span>郡山四月樱花开</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"></span></font></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"> </font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"></font></span> </p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://1842.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2010/4/24/20/14/128e269380bg215.jpg\" style=\"display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;text-align:center\"><font size=\"4\"></font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><span>雪花不请竟自来</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"></span></font></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"> </font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"></font></span> </p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://1812.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2010/4/24/20/15/128e269c46dg213.jpg\" style=\"display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;text-align:center\"><font size=\"4\"></font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><span>风中犹感春意冷</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"></span></font></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"> </font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"></font></span> </p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://1852.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2010/4/24/20/15/128e26a0da5g215.jpg\" style=\"display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;text-align:center\"><font size=\"4\"></font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><span>樱花淡粉雪花白</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"></span></font></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"> </font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://1872.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2010/4/24/20/16/128e26a909bg213.jpg\" style=\"display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;text-align:center\"><font size=\"4\"></font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><span>难得相约在春季</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"></span></font></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"> </font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://1832.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2010/4/24/20/16/128e26ad1b0g215.jpg\" style=\"display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;text-align:center\"><font size=\"4\"></font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><span>绚丽多彩同出台</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"></span></font></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"> </font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://512.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2010/4/24/20/16/128e26b2c77g215.jpg\" style=\"display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;text-align:center\"><font size=\"4\"></font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><span>今日留得美景在</span></font><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"> </font></span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><span>明天流水与花骸</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"></span></font></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"> </font></span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><font size=\"4\"> </font></span></p>\n</div>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}